<subSubSection pageId="37" pageNumber="166" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="37.[1441,2649,300,1161]" pageId="37" pageNumber="166">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1444,1795,931,960]" pageId="37" pageNumber="166">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Mcllhenny’s Four-eyed Opossum has a wide distribution and presumably a large overall population.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
